import React from "react";
import { TextField, Button, Container, Grid } from "@mui/material";

const MyForm = () => {
  const handleSubmit = (event) => {
    event.preventDefault();
    // Add your form submission logic here
  };

  return (
    <Container>
      <form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField
              required
              fullWidth
              label="Name"
              variant="outlined"
              margin="normal"
              // Add any other props you need
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField
              required
              fullWidth
              label="Email"
              variant="outlined"
              margin="normal"
              type="email"
              // Add any other props you need
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField
              required
              fullWidth
              label="Telephone"
              variant="outlined"
              margin="normal"
              // Add any other props you need
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField
              required
              fullWidth
              label="X"
              variant="outlined"
              margin="normal"
              // Add any other props you need
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField
              required
              fullWidth
              label="Y"
              variant="outlined"
              margin="normal"
              // Add any other props you need
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Button type="submit" variant="contained" color="primary">
              Submit
            </Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </form>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default MyForm;
